result:
<van-tabbar
	route
	v-model="mActive"
	@change="$emit('footBarChange',mActive)"
	active-color="#FF500A"
	inactive-color="#333"
	class="footBar"
>
	<van-tabbar-item
		v-for="(footBar,index) in footBarItems"
		:key="index"
		:name="footBar.name"
		:icon="mActive === footBar.name ? footBar.icon[1] : footBar.icon[0]"
		:to="footBar.to"
	>
		{{footBar.text}}
	</van-tabbar-item>
</van-tabbar>
